A cikin kwata na biyu na 2018 kadai, an samu kusan sabbin mutane 40,000 da suka kamu da cutar.
Yawancin sabbin cututtukan sun kasance saboda kamuwa da cutar ta hanyar jima'i, wanda ya canza daga abin da ya gabata.
A al'adance, cutar HIV ta yadu cikin sauri a wasu sassan kasar Sin ta hanyar jini.
Amma, an rage yawan masu dauke da cutar HIV zuwa kusan babu, a cewar jami'an kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin a wani taro a lardin Yunnan.
Ko da yake, a kowace shekara, yawan mutanen da ke rayuwa da cutar kanjamau da cutar kanjamau a kasar Sin na ƙaruwa da mutane 100,000.
Cutar kwayar cutar kanjamau ta hanyar jima'i babbar matsala ce a tsakanin 'yan luwadi da mata masu jima'i a China.
A shekarar 1997, an halatta luwadi a kasar Sin, amma har yanzu ana nuna bambanci ga LGBT.
Saboda dabi'un kasar na kiyayewa, bincike ya nuna cewa kashi 70 zuwa 90 cikin 100 na maza suna yin jima'i da maza, sai su auri mata.
Yawancin cututtuka da yawa suna zuwa ne daga rashin isasshen jima'i a cikin wannan dangantaka.
Tun daga 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samar da magani ga cutar HIV ga kowa a kasar a matsayin wani bangare na kokarin magance matsalar.
Maxine Waters ya musanta 'tsarin ƙarya' da 'ra'ayoyin da' yan majalisar GOP suka yi
A ranar Asabar, 'yar Republican Maxine Waters ta yi watsi da zargin da aka yi mata cewa wani ma'aikacinta ya wallafa bayanan sirri na 'yan majalisar dattawa uku na Republican a shafinsa na Wikipedia.
The Los Angeles Democrat ya yi ikirarin cewa waɗannan maganganun suna da yawa daga masana "masu ra'ayin gurguzu" da kuma shafukan yanar gizo.
"Karya, ƙarya da ƙara ƙara ƙyamar ƙarya", Waters ya ce a cikin wata sanarwa a shafin Twitter.
Bayanan da aka bayyana sun hada da adireshin gida da lambobin waya na Sanatocin Amurka, Sanata Lindsey Graham na South Carolina, da Mike Lee da Orin Hatch, duka Utah.
Wannan bayanin ya bayyana a yanar gizo a ranar Alhamis, lokacin da wani mutum da ba a san ko wane ne ba a kan Capitol Hill ya wallafa shi a lokacin da ake sauraron karar da aka shigar a gaban kwamitin majalisar dattijai kan zargin cin zarafin da aka yi wa Brett Kavanaugh, wanda aka zaɓa a matsayin dan takarar Kotun Koli.
Wannan ya faru ne jim kadan bayan da aka yi wa Sanata Kavanaugh tambayoyi.
Shafukan da ke da ra'ayin mazan jiya kamar Gateway Pundit da Redsted sun ce adireshin IP da ke gano tushen sakon yana da alaƙa da ofishin Waters kuma ya ba da labarin wasu ma'aikatan Waters, Hill ya ruwaito.
"Wannan zargi marar tushe karya ne kuma karya ne", Waters ya ci gaba.
"Wani ma'aikacinmu - wanda ya sa aka yi wa mutuncinsa, bayanansa da kuma tsaronsa barazana ta hanyar wannan zamba da kuma karya - ba shi da alhakin wannan ɓoyewa.
Wannan zargi marar tushe ba daidai ba ne kuma ƙarya ne".
Sanarwar Waters ta jawo suka daga mutane da yawa a kan layi, ciki har da tsohon sakataren watsa labarai na fadar White House, Ari Fleischer.
"Wannan ƙin yarda yana da haushi", in ji Fleisher.
"Wannan ya nuna cewa ba shi da burin zama dan majalisa.
Ba sa fushi idan aka zargi su da wani abin da ba su yi ba.
Ba za su yi jayayya ba.
Bai kamata su yi tambaya game da manufar mai gabatar da ƙarar ba.
Dole ne su kasance masu natsuwa da nutsuwa".
A lokacin da Alkalin Kotun ya yi ta kwatanta yadda Waters ya yi da yadda 'yan Democrat suka soki Kavanaugh, masu sukar sun ce ya fusata sosai a lokacin da aka yi shari'ar a ranar Alhamis.
Dan takarar jam'iyyar Republican Omar Navarro, wanda ke neman tsige Waters a zaben fidda gwani, shi ma ya bayyana ra'ayinsa a shafinsa na Twitter.
"Wannan babban abu ne idan gaskiya ne", in ji shi a shafinsa na Twitter.
A cikin sanarwar da ta fitar, Waters ta ce ofishinta ya gargadi hukumomi da hukumomin da suka dace da hukumomin tsaro game da wannan ikirarin na yaudara.
"Za mu tabbatar da cewa za a gano masu laifin", ya ci gaba, "kuma za a hukunta su bisa doka saboda duk ayyukan da suka aikata wadanda ke da lahani da kuma hatsari ga kowane memba na ma'aikatana".
Johnny English ya sake yin bita - Rashin Rowan Atkinson na leken asiri
Yanzu al'ada ce a ga mahimmancin Brexit a kowane sabon fim tare da yanayin Biritaniya, kuma wannan ya shafi sake farfadowa na Johnny English action-comedy spoof franchise - wanda ya fara da Johnny English a 2003 kuma ya dawo cikin Johnny English Reborn a 2011.
Shin wannan abin dariya da muke yi game da yadda muke da kyau zai zama wata dama ta fitarwa?
A duk lokacin da yake raye, Johnny English mai kallon ido, mai kallon roba, yana da lasisi don ƙirƙirar sabon abu a karo na biyu - fiye da duk abin da sunansa ya nuna, yana da kwarewar zane-zane da aka tsara don fina-finai a cikin harsunan da ba Turanci ba.
Ya kasance mai ba da shawara ga wakilin ɓoye mara kyau wanda ya ɗan ɗaure duk da ƙarancin saurin saurin saurin saurin saurin saurin saurin saurin sa, wani dash na Mr. Bean da dolop na Chap ya ba da gudummawa ga waƙar taken Sheriots of Fire a cikin waƙar bikin buɗe wasannin Olympics na 2012 a London.
Ya yi wasa da yawa a kan Traveller da kuma a kan Atkinson, mutumin da ya ɓoye asirinsa na duniya, a cikin wani abin da aka manta da shi a cikin Barclaycard TV, yana yada rikici a cikin hikima.
Akwai wani abu ko biyu da suka faru a wannan taron.
Na ji daɗin ganin Johnny English yana zuwa wurin jirgin sama da ke ɗauke da ƙaramin kwalkwali da kuma ruwan da ke ɗauke da ƙananan kwalkwali.
Duk da haka, an ji daɗin daɗaɗawa da kuma ban mamaki, musamman ma irin wannan "mai tsanani" fim din kamar 007 da kuma Mission Impossible yanzu suna ba da kyauta tare da amincewa.
Wasan kwaikwayo ya fi dacewa da yara fiye da manya, kuma a gare ni, Johnny English ba shi da mahimmanci ba ne a cikin abubuwan da suka faru a cikin Binn, kamar yadda Atkinson ya yi a cikin fina-finai na fim din.
A cikin shekaru da yawa, abin da ya fi dacewa shi ne cewa Birtaniya na cikin matsala.
Wani dan damfara na yanar gizo ya shiga cikin wani gidan yanar gizo na leken asiri na kasar Birtaniya, domin ya fallasa dukkan jami'an Birtaniya da ke aiki a wannan fannin, don ya batawa jami'an da ke da alhakin - wani abin takaici ga Kevin Eldon.
Wannan shi ne na karshe na wani firaministan kasar da ya riga ya sha wahala daga rashin jituwa, mai ban tsoro da kuma mai hankali: Emma Thompson ta yi fice a wannan rawar da ake yi wa Theresa May, amma ba a yi wani abu mai yawa a cikin rubutun ba.
Masu ba shi shawara sun gaya masa cewa an lalata dukan masu leƙen asirin da suke aiki a dā, saboda haka, ya kamata ya sa wani ya yi murabus.
Kuma wannan yana nufin cewa Johnny English, wanda yanzu yana aiki a matsayin malami a wata makarantar fasikanci, ya koyar da yadda ake yin aiki a karkashin wani abin da ba a sani ba: akwai wasu kyawawan abubuwa masu ban dariya, tun da yake English yana ba da makarantar makarantar jami'a ta jami'a.
