Menene bikin 'yan ƙasa na duniya kuma shin ya yi wani abu don rage talauci?
A wannan Asabar a New York za a yi bikin 'yan kasa na duniya, wani taron kiɗa na shekara-shekara wanda ke da kyakkyawan jerin gwanon wasan kwaikwayo na taurari da kuma manufa mai ban sha'awa; kawo karshen talauci a duniya.
Yanzu a shekara ta bakwai, Bikin 'Yan Kasa na Duniya zai ga dubban mutane suna yawo a Babban Launin Central Park don jin daɗin ayyukan kamar Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes, ba don kawai ba, amma don wayar da kan jama'a game da ainihin burin taron na kawo ƙarshen matsanancin talauci nan da 2030.
An bayyana a cikin 2012, bikin na 'yan kasa na duniya shine fadada shirin talauci na duniya, ƙungiyar da ke neman kawar da talauci ta hanyar haɓaka yawan mutanen da ke gwagwarmayar yin gwagwarmaya a duniya.
Don samun tikiti kyauta ga taron (idan ba ku da niyyar biyan kuɗin tikiti na VIP), masu ba da izini sun yi ayyuka da yawa ko "aikin" kamar aikin sa kai, aikawa da shugaban duniya, yin kira ta waya ko wasu hanyoyi masu ma'ana don taimakawa wajen wayar da kan jama'a game da burinsu na kawo ƙarshen talauci.
Amma yaya Global Citizen ya yi nasara a shekara 12 da suka rage kafin ya cimma burinsa?
Shin ra'ayin da ya bayar da lada ga mutane ta hanyar wasan kwaikwayo kyauta shine ainihin abin da ya kamata ya sa mutane su yi kira don yin aiki, ko kuma wani lamari ne na abin da ake kira "clicktivism" - inda mutane suke jin cewa suna yin bambanci ta hanyar sanya hannu a kan takarda kai ta kan layi ko aikawa da tweet?
Tun daga 2011, Global Citizen ta ce ta yi rikodin "aiki" sama da miliyan 19 daga magoya bayanta, suna ci gaba da cimma burinsu.
Ya ce, wadannan matakan sun taimaka wa shugabannin duniya su yi alkawarin dalar Amurka biliyan 37 da kuma manufofi da za su shafi rayukan mutane biliyan 2.22 nan da shekarar 2030.
A farkon 2018, kungiyar ta yi nuni da alkawura da sanarwar 390 da suka fara daga ayyukanta, wanda akalla dala biliyan 10 aka riga aka rarraba ko kuma aka tara.
Kungiyar ta kiyasta cewa asusun da aka tanada ya kai wa mutane miliyan 649 a duniya kai tsaye.
Wasu daga cikin manyan alkawuran sun hada da Power of Nutrition, wani haɗin gwiwa na masu saka jari da masu aiwatarwa na Burtaniya wanda ke da alhakin "taimakawa yara suyi amfani da cikakkiyar damar su", tare da alƙawarin samar da miliyan 35 ga Ruwanda don kawo ƙarshen matsalar rashin abinci mai gina jiki a County bayan da aka karɓi tweets sama da 4,700 daga Global Citizen.
"Tare da taimakon gwamnatin Burtaniya, masu ba da gudummawa, gwamnatoci na ƙasa da ƙasa, da 'yan ƙasa na duniya kamar ku, za mu iya sanya rashin lafiyar rashin abinci mai gina jiki a cikin tarihin", in ji Tracey Woolman, jakadan The Power of Nutrition, a lokacin wani taron jama'a a watan Afrilu 2018 a London.
Kungiyar ta kuma ce bayan da aka dauki matakai sama da 5,000 a Amurka don inganta abinci mai gina jiki na iyaye da jarirai, gwamnati ta sanar da biyan kudade don wani shiri, The Power of Nutrition, wanda zai kai mata da yara miliyan 5 a cikin aikin abinci mai gina jiki.
Tambayar da aka yi a shafinta ta yanar gizo ita ce, "Me kuke ganin zai iya kawo karshen matsanancin talauci?"
Global Citizen ya amsa: "Hanya mai tsawo ce da kuma wahala - wani lokaci za mu yi kasawa mu kuma yi kasawa.
Amma, kamar yadda yake a manyan ƙungiyoyin kare haƙƙin jama'a da kuma ƙiyayya da wariyar launin fata, za mu yi nasara, domin tare muna da ƙarfi.
