Amurka za ta iya amfani da sojan ruwa don hana Rasha fitar da mai - Sakataren Cikin Gida
Sakataren cikin gida na Amurka Ryan Zinke ya bayyana cewa Washington na iya amfani da jiragen ruwanta idan ya "dace" don hana masu jigilar makamashin Rasha shiga kasashen Gabas ta Tsakiya.
