An sake dakatar da sabon jirgin ruwan Jamus
An shirya shirin da za a fara aiki a shekarar 2014 tare da sabon rukunin jiragen ruwan na rundunar sojin ruwan Jamus, wanda zai maye gurbin tsohon jirgin ruwan yakin Cold War, amma ba zai yiwu ba har zuwa shekara mai zuwa saboda tsarin da ba shi da kyau da kuma tsadar da ake kashewa wajen yin amfani da shi.
Jaridar Die Zeit ta ruwaito wani mai magana da yawun rundunar sojan kasar ya ce, an dage kaddamar da jirgin farko na sabon Baden-Württemberg-class na Rhineland-Pfalz zuwa farkon shekarar 2019.
An shirya za a shigar da jirgin ruwan a cikin 2014, amma an dakatar da wannan aikin mai ban sha'awa saboda matsalolin da aka samu bayan isarwa.
Jiragen ruwa guda huɗu na Baden-Württemberg da rundunar sojan ruwa ta ba da umarnin a 2007 za su maye gurbin tsofaffin jiragen ruwa na Bremen.
An ba da rahoton cewa za su sami manyan bindigogi, anti-aircraft da anti-ship missiles da kuma wasu fasahohin ɓoye kamar rage radar, infrared da siginar siginar.
