Sabuntawar Ruwa mai laushi: Ragewar Ruwa a Pinellas, Manauta da Sarasota
Wani sabon rahoto daga Hukumar Kifi da namun daji ta Florida ya nuna cewa akwai raguwar jan ruwa a yankin Tampa Bay.
A cewar FWC, akwai yanayin fure na pachyon a Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte, da kuma Coalier Counties - alamar alamun raguwar taro.
Ruwan Ruwa na Ruwa yana da nisan kilomita 130 na gabar teku daga Pinellas a arewa zuwa Lee County a kudu.
Ana iya ganin patches kusan mil 10 daga bakin rairayin bakin teku a Hillsborough County, amma ba a lura da shi ba fiye da makon da ya gabata.
An samu karuwar ruwan sama a yankin Pasco.
A cikin makon da ya gabata, an samu matsakaicin yawa a bakin teku da kuma nesa da bakin teku a gundumar Pinellas, ƙananan zuwa mafi girma a bakin teku a gundumar Hillsboro, mafi girma a cikin gundumar Manatee, mafi girma a bakin teku da kuma nesa a gundumar Sarasota, matsakaici a gundumar Charlotte, mafi yawa a bakin teku da kuma nisa a gundumar Lee, da kuma ƙananan a cikin gundumar Collier.
Ana ci gaba da samun rahotannin cututtukan numfashi daga Pinellas, Manatee da Sarasota, Lee da Collier Counties.
Ba a samu rahoton wani sabon kamuwa da cutar numfashi ba a yankin arewa maso yammacin Florida a cikin makon da ya gabata.
